name: Stray Cat
text: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 "Stray Cat" from your hand. While this card is in face-up Attack Position, your opponent's monsters cannot target monsters for attacks, except this one. When this card is destroyed by battle and sent to the Graveyard: You can Special Summon 1 "Monster Cat" from your hand, Deck, or Graveyard.
